{"TopicId":204196,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"\u0027Warp to sunrise\u0027 button hindering use of \u0027Tool: Place\u0027 (EVA Construction Mode)","CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-04T19:28:27Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"swjr-swis","CreatedById":152460,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-04T19:28:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nCan the construction mode gizmo buttons be moved slightly to the right, so the \u0027warp to sunrise\u0027 button doesn\u0027t constantly eclipse \u0027Tool: Place\u0027 whenever we get our cursor anywhere near it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s like those boxes with a switch that you can never keep flipped because a finger keeps coming out to immediately flip it back...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 alt=\u0022qfwKQh5.png\u0022 src=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/qfwKQh5.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222021-08-04T23:30:47Z\u0022 title=\u002208/04/2021 11:30  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00222 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 4, 2021\u003C/time\u003E by swjr-swis\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Etyops; screenshot added\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Aziz","CreatedById":150811,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-10T06:45:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://bugs.kerbalspaceprogram.com/issues/28113\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://bugs.kerbalspaceprogram.com/issues/28113\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Admiral Fluffy","CreatedById":210816,"CreatedDateTime":"2021-08-13T16:19:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-co